<graph edgedefault="undirected"><node id="Куба">
  <data key="d0">Куба</data>
  <data key="d1">country</data>
  <data key="d2">Куба is a country experiencing widespread protests, power outages, and arson attacks on government institutions.&lt;SEP&gt;Куба is a country subject to a U.S. energy blockade since January 2026, which has led to widespread blackouts, and is listed by the U.S. Treasury as prohibited from receiving Russian oil.&lt;SEP&gt;Куба is a country that held secret negotiations with the United States in Havana, facing economic decline and pressure for democratic and economic reforms.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9d076bc578a76f0d37205d88cb111e3a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-33fbdbc87dc3d63c894c4967c64e416d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6d798b538fd8af34e3a1e68772e086e8</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Куба\5.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Куба\6.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Куба\8.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777422364</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
  <data key="d7">Куба</data>
</node>
<node id="Коммунистическая партия Кубы">
  <data key="d0">Коммунистическая партия Кубы</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Коммунистическая партия Кубы is the ruling political party in Куба, with local offices targeted and set on fire by protesters.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9d076bc578a76f0d37205d88cb111e3a</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Куба\5.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777417868</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Президент Кубы">
  <data key="d0">Президент Кубы</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Президент Кубы is the leader who announced the initiation of negotiations with the United States, triggering further public unrest.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9d076bc578a76f0d37205d88cb111e3a</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Куба\5.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777417868</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="США">
  <data key="d0">США</data>
  <data key="d1">country</data>
  <data key="d2">США is the foreign nation with which Куба's president has announced the start of negotiations.&lt;SEP&gt;США is referenced by Александр Дугин as a geopolitical adversary seeking influence over post-Soviet states.&lt;SEP&gt;США is a country that conducted secret negotiations with Куба, proposing the lifting of trade embargoes and access to Starlink in exchange for political and economic reforms.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9d076bc578a76f0d37205d88cb111e3a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d87de5ac222f3f5483a17dcd9be1a802&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6d798b538fd8af34e3a1e68772e086e8</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Куба\5.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Ультра левые и ультра правые\10.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Куба\8.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777422364</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
  <data key="d7">США</data>
</node>
<node id="Протесты на Кубе">
  <data key="d0">Протесты на Кубе</data>
  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">Протесты на Кубе are widespread demonstrations accompanied by arson and prolonged electricity blackouts.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9d076bc578a76f0d37205d88cb111e3a</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Куба\5.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777417868</data>
