</node>
<node id="Дональд Трамп">
  <data key="d0">Дональд Трамп</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Дональд Трамп is the President of the United States who stated that he does not object to the delivery of Russian oil to Cuba, despite the energy blockade, and criticized Cuba's regime as corrupt and unsustainable.&lt;SEP&gt;Дональд Трамп is the former U.S. president who used military force to remove Venezuela's leader Nicolás Maduro and threatened to annex Greenland, prompting reactions from Europe's far-right parties.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-33fbdbc87dc3d63c894c4967c64e416d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-19d93fe51122c951f011d35eb337a3f7</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Куба\6.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Ультра левые и ультра правые\9.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777422382</data>
