  <data key="d1">equipment</data>
  <data key="d2">Російський нафтовий танкер is a Russian oil tanker carrying approximately 730,000 barrels of oil destined for Куба, scheduled to arrive on March 31, 2026.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-33fbdbc87dc3d63c894c4967c64e416d</data>
