  <data key="d0">Енергетична блокада</data>
  <data key="d1">conflict</data>
  <data key="d2">Енергетична блокада is the U.S.-imposed restriction on oil shipments to Куба, enacted in January 2026, resulting in two total blackouts on the island.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-33fbdbc87dc3d63c894c4967c64e416d</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Куба\6.txt</data>
