  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Мінфін США is the U.S. Department of the Treasury that added Куба to a list of countries prohibited from receiving Russian oil.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-33fbdbc87dc3d63c894c4967c64e416d</data>
