  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Ґрета Тунберг is collaborating with Italian far-left allies to launch a campaign against the militarization of Europe.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-47985507480c716e0000b869ef2c9aa6</data>
