<node id="Украина">
  <data key="d0">Украина</data>
  <data key="d1">country</data>
  <data key="d2">Ukraine is the country where German soldiers from the Bundeswehr are proposed to be deployed in a peacekeeping capacity.&lt;SEP&gt;Украина is the target of Russia’s military advances, facing expected collapse of its defense and state institutions, but is being supported by Western allies to strengthen its military and resilience.&lt;SEP&gt;Ukraine is the recipient of Western arms shipments, details of which are among the classified information reportedly leaked by АдГ.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9bd051cb787992a9c82372f39a42ff14&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fc81f47105f95a01062a3dca9ee5ad14&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-96d3d395cd55743faf41e3b3b3a8d446</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Ультра левые и ультра правые\3.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Ультра левые и ультра правые\4.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Ультра левые и ультра правые\19.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777418254</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Зеленые">
  <data key="d0">Зеленые</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Зеленые is a German political party whose supporters most strongly favor deploying Bundeswehr soldiers in Ukraine.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9bd051cb787992a9c82372f39a42ff14</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Ультра левые и ультра правые\3.txt</data>
