<node id="АдГ">
  <data key="d0">АдГ</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">АдГ is a German political party with the highest number of opponents to deploying Bundeswehr soldiers in Ukraine.&lt;SEP&gt;АдГ is a far-right German political party suspected of transmitting classified European Union documents to Russia.&lt;SEP&gt;АдГ is a far-right group in Germany with overlapping membership and ideological ties to Atomwaffen Division, as indicated by arrests during investigations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9bd051cb787992a9c82372f39a42ff14&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-96d3d395cd55743faf41e3b3b3a8d446&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4117a24ac776e64ee5b10c9c825a2778</data>
