<node id="Путин">
  <data key="d0">Путин</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Путин is the leader of Russia who openly declares Russia's military intentions, seeks to expand control over Ukrainian territories, and aims to influence European politics by promoting ultraleft and ultraright populists.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-fc81f47105f95a01062a3dca9ee5ad14</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Ультра левые и ультра правые\4.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777417989</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Белоусов">
  <data key="d0">Белоусов</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Белоусов is a Russian official who, alongside Путин, outlines Russia’s military plans for 2026–2030, including the expansion of the SVO goals and preparation for conflict with NATO.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-fc81f47105f95a01062a3dca9ee5ad14</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Ультра левые и ультра правые\4.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777417989</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Россия">
  <data key="d0">Россия</data>
  <data key="d1">country</data>
  <data key="d2">Россия is a country pursuing a long-term military strategy to achieve its "SVO objectives," expand its buffer zone in Ukraine, and prepare for potential conflict with NATO by 2030.&lt;SEP&gt;Russia is accused of receiving classified information from members of the German far-right party АдГ, including details on defense systems and Western military aid to Ukraine.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-fc81f47105f95a01062a3dca9ee5ad14&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-96d3d395cd55743faf41e3b3b3a8d446</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Ультра левые и ультра правые\4.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Ультра левые и ультра правые\19.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777418254</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="НАТО">
  <data key="d0">НАТО</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">НАТО is a military alliance that Russia claims is preparing to attack it by the 2030s, though Russia frames its own actions as defensive.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-fc81f47105f95a01062a3dca9ee5ad14</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Ультра левые и ультра правые\4.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777417989</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="СВО">
  <data key="d0">СВО</data>
  <data key="d1">conflict</data>
  <data key="d2">СВО (специальная военная операция) is Russia’s stated military campaign aimed at securing "historical lands" in Ukraine, with objectives extending beyond Donbas to include Sumy and Kharkiv.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-fc81f47105f95a01062a3dca9ee5ad14</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Ультра левые и ультра правые\4.txt</data>
