  <data key="d0">2026–2030 Military Plan</data>
  <data key="d1">document</data>
  <data key="d2">The 2026–2030 Military Plan is Russia’s strategic outline for sustained military operations in Ukraine and preparation for confrontation with NATO, presented by Путин and Белоусов.</data>
