  <data key="d2">Greenland is a territory sought by Donald Trump for control, viewed by Europe as outside U.S. sphere of influence.&lt;SEP&gt;Greenland is a territory where Trump is alleged to have violated sovereignty, according to Alice Weidel.</data>
