<node id="Russia">
  <data key="d0">Russia</data>
  <data key="d1">country</data>
  <data key="d2">Russia is the country whose state-owned enterprises (Gazprom, RZhD) are suffering financial losses due to war, and whose shadow fleet vessels have been targeted by the United States.&lt;SEP&gt;Russia is a country that Alice Weidel asserts must be included in any viable peace agreement for Europe.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-247e3564ae01c87b4e47bbb7579416ea&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-98d518fc3b7e7fe3dcf675759a3da1ed&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2802e11b74b9768fe90d58d3fe517040&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-261d8bd00caff040b0b682991d5548c5</data>
