<node id="United States">
  <data key="d0">United States</data>
  <data key="d1">country</data>
  <data key="d2">The United States conducted operations against the Russian shadow fleet, detained vessels Bella 1 and Sophia, and expressed interest in Greenland as part of its strategic positioning.&lt;SEP&gt;The United States is the primary origin of the modern white jihad movement, driven by American white supremacists and later adopted by European far-right groups.&lt;SEP&gt;The United States is implementing new tariffs on goods from countries that supply oil to Cuba, as a national security measure.</data>
