  <data key="d0">Alice Weidel</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Alice Weidel is the leader of the German far-right AfD party who criticizes double standards in international reactions to sovereignty violations by Putin and Trump.&lt;SEP&gt;Alice Weidel is a prominent AfD figure and a close political ally of Marcus Frontmayr.&lt;SEP&gt;Alice Weidel is the leader of the German AfD who calls for peace negotiations between Ukraine and Russia and criticizes Western opposition to diplomacy.</data>
