  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">AfD is a German far-right political party led by Alice Weidel.&lt;SEP&gt;AfD is a political party in Germany that has been involved in scandals related to nepotism at both state and federal levels, despite positioning itself as opposed to party favoritism.&lt;SEP&gt;AfD (Alternative for Germany) is a political party in Germany whose voters overwhelmingly reject any support for Ukraine, with 65% opposing aid.</data>
