  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">Baden-Württemberg is a German federal state where Marcus Frontmayr is a leading candidate for AfD.&lt;SEP&gt;Baden-Württemberg is a German federal state where the antiterrorism center SAT BW is located and where extremist activities linked to Atomwaffen Division and Terrorgram-сцена have been monitored.</data>
