<node id="Ursula von der Leyen">
  <data key="d0">Ursula von der Leyen</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Ursula von der Leyen is the President of the European Commission and a representative of the center-right European People's Party, serving as a central figure in European political establishment and a target of criticism from both far-right and far-left factions.&lt;SEP&gt;Ursula von der Leyen is the President of the European Commission, facing multiple motions of censure between 2025 and 2026.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ffb76e13354613b80f653af13be1e243&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9537adb639f6d92a3c655a2e0dc6a434</data>
