</node>
<node id="Pfizergate">
  <data key="d0">Pfizergate</data>
  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">Pfizergate is a scandal involving non-transparent, multi-billion euro vaccine procurement deals during the COVID-19 pandemic, conducted via private SMS messages between von der Leyen’s administration and Pfizer’s CEO.&lt;SEP&gt;Pfizergate refers to allegations of opacity in COVID-19 vaccine procurement, triggering a motion of censure against the von der Leyen Commission in July 2025.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ffb76e13354613b80f653af13be1e243&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9537adb639f6d92a3c655a2e0dc6a434</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Ультра левые и ультра правые\20.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Ультра левые и ультра правые\21.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777418926</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Europes Fortress">
  <data key="d0">Europes Fortress</data>
  <data key="d1">policy</data>
  <data key="d2">Europes Fortress refers to the EU’s migration control strategy involving financial agreements with authoritarian regimes like Tunisia and Egypt to intercept migrants, criticized by the far-left as a human rights violation.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ffb76e13354613b80f653af13be1e243</data>
