</node>
<node id="Gaza Conflict">
  <data key="d0">Gaza Conflict</data>
  <data key="d1">conflict</data>
  <data key="d2">The Gaza Conflict is a military and humanitarian crisis in which Israel’s actions are supported by Ursula von der Leyen, leading to accusations of complicity in violations of international law.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ffb76e13354613b80f653af13be1e243</data>
