<node id="Pfizer">
  <data key="d0">Pfizer</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Pfizer is a multinational pharmaceutical corporation involved in the Pfizergate scandal through non-transparent vaccine procurement deals with the European Commission.&lt;SEP&gt;Pfizer is a pharmaceutical company implicated in the Pfizergate scandal over opaque vaccine procurement practices.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ffb76e13354613b80f653af13be1e243&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9537adb639f6d92a3c655a2e0dc6a434</data>
