<node id="Motion of Censure">
  <data key="d0">Motion of Censure</data>
  <data key="d1">document</data>
  <data key="d2">A motion of censure is a formal legal instrument in the European Parliament that, if passed, requires the entire European Commission to resign.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9537adb639f6d92a3c655a2e0dc6a434</data>
