<node id="Atomwaffen Division">
  <data key="d0">Atomwaffen Division</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Atomwaffen Division is a transnational neo-Nazi network promoting white supremacy, blending it with salafist national-socialist ideology, "white jihad," and accelerationist terrorism; it supports Hamas, Al-Qaeda, and ISIS, operates as a decentralized online network, and inspires lone-actor attacks through digital propaganda and gamified violence.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4117a24ac776e64ee5b10c9c825a2778</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Ультра левые и ультра правые\22.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777419333</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Terrorgram-сцена">
  <data key="d0">Terrorgram-сцена</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Terrorgram-сцена is a decentralized far-right extremist online network, primarily on Telegram, inspired by Atomwaffen Division, characterized by shared ideology, aesthetic, and digital practices mirroring jihadist media and strategies, including "white sharia" and martyr cults.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4117a24ac776e64ee5b10c9c825a2778</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Ультра левые и ультра правые\22.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777419333</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Hamas">
  <data key="d0">Hamas</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Hamas is a jihadist organization supported by Atomwaffen Division and referenced within far-right extremist circles as an ideological ally in the context of shared enemies.&lt;SEP&gt;Hamas is a Palestinian Islamist organization that published and distributed David Myatt’s works, recognizing him as an authoritative Islamist voice.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4117a24ac776e64ee5b10c9c825a2778&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4698e80f89aaeb2bfe1d0d03eef662a4</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Ультра левые и ультра правые\22.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Ультра левые и ультра правые\23.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777419918</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Al-Qaeda">
  <data key="d0">Al-Qaeda</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Al-Qaeda is a jihadist organization supported by Atomwaffen Division and referenced within far-right extremist circles as an ideological ally in the context of shared enemies.&lt;SEP&gt;Al-Qaeda is a global jihadist organization that received financial support from Al-Taqwa Bank and had ideological and operational links with Aryan Nations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4117a24ac776e64ee5b10c9c825a2778&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4698e80f89aaeb2bfe1d0d03eef662a4</data>
