<node id="SAFE">
  <data key="d0">SAFE</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">SAFE is the antiterrorism center of Baden-Württemberg (SAT BW) that published a 2025 report documenting the convergence of neo-Nazi and jihadist extremist ideologies in Germany.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4117a24ac776e64ee5b10c9c825a2778</data>
