<node id="Поступь Астреи">
  <data key="d0">Поступь Астреи</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Поступь Астреи is a source that forwards content related to extremist ideologies, including white jihadism and neo-Nazi movements.&lt;SEP&gt;Поступь Астреи is the source channel that forwarded the original post discussing the convergence of far-right and jihadist ideologies.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e9a14fc1e13b7bdf9ed3cf57cf0801e3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4698e80f89aaeb2bfe1d0d03eef662a4</data>
