  <data key="d1">document</data>
  <data key="d2">Are Martyrdom Operations Lawful According to the Qur’an and Sunnah? is a treatise by David Myatt that attempts to legitimize suicide attacks through Islamic jurisprudence, bridging neo-Nazi and jihadist ideologies.</data>
