<node id="Trumps Greenland Play Is a Step Too Far for Europes Far Right">
  <data key="d0">Trumps Greenland Play Is a Step Too Far for Europes Far Right</data>
  <data key="d1">document</data>
  <data key="d2">Trump’s Greenland Play Is a Step Too Far for Europe’s Far Right is an article by Bloomberg discussing the political backlash in Europe to Trump’s interest in annexing Greenland.</data>
